<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Belam No Thihna Lopi</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka Lal Kraws chu ka ngaisang pen,
 Khawvel sum chu ka ngainep hi;
 Ziechun aw nam chitin cheng din,
 Kipahna bukim a um hi.

[V2]
 Aw, ka ngaina ie pak bang chawi ing ka.
 Ka Lalpa Kraws chu ka bitna pen;
 Lungkham chate Nangmah vangin ,
 Ka ma lamah Aw, lawpna'n kawl a eng.

[V3]
 2. Khawvel hawihna leh lopina,
 Etin lungkham a khawk diek ie;
 Kumsawt a ka thagau chawl leh,
 Kipahna dang him mu puong ka.

[V4]
 3. Gitloh huihpi van nim lakah ,
 Leh gal maa ka din kuomin;
 Ka kulhpi leh ka bitna pen,
 Kalvari Thing ka ngai na ie.

[V5]
 4. Tuisuohgiet van leh khawvel in ,
 Belam No thihna lopi chu;
 Pak zaila sau hen kumsawt in,
 Hallelui, Halleluijah Amen.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>141</hymn_number>
</song>